ce it unconditionally, immediately copy it back, or perform some sort of \"merge\" operation on it.  This can be confusing for the administrator, who is likely to expect it to behave like the configuration files for other daemons on the system.\n\nPackaged software generally handles changed config files by either not touching them (e.g. creating eucalyptus.conf.rpmnew instead) or using a standard mechanism like debconf.\n","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=gholmstrom","name":"gholmstrom","key":"gholmstrom","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d1457b72c3fb323a2671125aef3eab5d?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FavatarId%3D10123%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d1457b72c3fb323a2671125aef3eab5d?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26avatarId%3D10123%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d1457b72c3fb323a2671125aef3eab5d?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26avatarId%3D10123%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d1457b72c3fb323a2671125aef3eab5d?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26avatarId%3D10123%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"gholmstrom","active":false,"timeZone":"US/Central"},"created":"2012-04-23T22:49:33.569-0500","updated":"2012-04-23T22:49:33.569-0500"},{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/12344/comment/23386","id":"23386","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=agrimm","name":"agrimm","key":"agrimm","accountId":"557058:9ebc3512-73d8-45c9-85de-4325aaa62488","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/0e947b5413f5d57fba29a8ea5412f773?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dagrimm%26avatarId%3D10500%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https